  ('social-worker-moex-07900', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '品質管理隨著時代的演進越來越重要，近二十年的品質管理主流是：', '["品管圈", "品質價值", "全面品質管理", "品質控制"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07901', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「服務只要有利基，有特定人群需要，就可以持續生存。冷門、規模小等並不嚴重，雖然只有少數人需要，但如果是 長期需要，也可以有利基」。這樣的經營策略稱之為：', '["定位策略", "藍海策略", "長尾巴理論", "創新策略"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07902', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '非營利組織需要有財務計畫，下列那一種計畫所涵蓋的期長可能是最長的（請選最適答案）？', '["現金預算計畫", "營運資金計畫", "資本預算計畫", "收支餘絀分析"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07903', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依照內政部所頒「社會團體財務處理辦法」之規定，社會團體年度業務費與辦公費支出不得少於總支出百分之多少？', '["30", "40", "50", "60"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6c91d4ef579", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "400", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
